<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>입출고 내역 - MediCare+</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/feather-icons"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  
  {{> components/sidebar}}

  <div class="main-content">
    {{> components/header}}
    
    <main class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
            <i data-feather="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">물품 입출고 내역</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">모든 물품의 입고 및 출고 기록을 확인합니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200 flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-50">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/items/history" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-slate-800 text-white">전체</a>
              <a href="/items/history?type=IN" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100">입고</a>
              <a href="/items/history?type=OUT" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100">출고</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="relative">
                <i data-feather="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                <form action="/items/history" method="GET">
                  <input type="text" name="search" placeholder="물품명 검색..." class="pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none w-64"/>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                <th class="p-4 font-medium">일시</th>
                <th class="p-4 font-medium">구분</th>
                <th class="p-4 font-medium">물품명</th>
                <th class="p-4 font-medium text-right">수량</th>
                <th class="p-4 font-medium">담당자</th>
                <th class="p-4 font-medium">비고</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
              {{#history}}
              <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">{{date}}</td>
                <td class="p-4">
                  {{#isIn}}
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                    <i data-feather="arrow-down-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>입고
                  </span>
                  {{/isIn}}
                  {{^isIn}}
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-red-100 text-red-800">
                    <i data-feather="arrow-up-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>출고
                  </span>
                  {{/isIn}}
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">{{itemName}}</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm font-bold text-right {{#isIn}}text-green-600{{/isIn}}{{^isIn}}text-red-600{{/isIn}}">
                  {{#isIn}}+{{/isIn}}{{^isIn}}-{{/isIn}}{{quantity}}
                </td>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">{{manager}}</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">{{note}}</td>
              </tr>
              {{/history}}

              {{^history}}
              <tr>
                <td colspan="6" class="p-8 text-center text-slate-500">
                  해당 조건의 입출고 내역이 없습니다.
                </td>
              </tr>
              {{/history}}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> components/footer}}
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      feather.replace();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>